<emphasis id="8E85EC65EF0367008773B4B10CB727E5" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Notes</emphasis>
. The location of the original material used for the description of 
<taxonomicName id="6495CC76157CB834B4ED4D4E279F9A8C" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="clausa">
